Abstract Construction Preverbal_Aspect_Marker
	subcase of Aspect_Marker


Abstract Construction Preverbal_Aspect_Marker_Root
	subcase of Morpheme, Preverbal_Aspect_Marker


Abstract Construction Postverbal_Aspect_Marker
