Construction Preverbal_Adverbial_Phrase
	subcase of Preverbal_Adverbial
	constructional
		constituents
			v : Verb	// this might be overly exclusive
			de : Associative_Marker
	form
		constraints
			v.f meets de.f
	meaning
		evokes Intransitive_State as ins
		constraints
			ins <--> v.m
			self.m.category <--> ins.category
	
	
Construction Stative_Associative
	subcase of Ref_Exp_Modifier
	constructional
		constituents
			v: Verb
			de: Nominalizer
	form
		constraints
			v.f meets de.f
	meaning
		evokes Intransitive_State as ins
		constraints
			ins <--> v.m
			ce <--> de.ce
			ce <--> v.m.protagonist
			self.m.category <--> ins.category


